articles.headline: CeeDee Lamb, in street garb, flagged after getting hit by official on sideline
articles.description: CeeDee Lamb took a big hit and committed a penalty in the Dallas Cowboys' preseason opener -- even though the star receiver wasn't playing.

images.name: CeeDee Lamb gets flagged after getting trucked by ref
images.caption: CeeDee Lamb is issued a penalty after a referee barrels into him on the sideline.

articles.headline: Titans rookie QB Cameron Ward leads TD drive in debut
articles.description: Titans rookie QB Cameron Ward made his preseason debut against the Tampa Bay Buccaneers on Saturday and showed promise in his first live game action.

images.name: Cam Ward connects with Calvin Ridley on his first 3 completions
images.caption: Cam Ward hits Calvin Ridley three times for 50 yards on a touchdown drive for the Titans.

articles.headline: Source: Packers' Jayden Reed dealing with sprained foot
articles.description: A source told ESPN's Adam Schefter that Packers WR Jayden Reed, who hasn't practiced since Wednesday, has a sprained foot and is day to day.

articles.headline: 'Nervous' Travis Hunter makes strong first impression with Jaguars
articles.description: Rookie receiver and cornerback Travis Hunter quieted the nerves with a strong first impression, playing 18 snaps in the Jaguars' 31-25 loss to the Pittsburgh Steelers on Saturday night.

images.name: Travis Hunter makes his first two catches on first preseason drive
images.caption: Travis Hunter makes a quick impact in the Jaguars' preseason opener with two catches on the first drive.

articles.headline: Stidham shines after Nix struggles as Broncos beat 49ers 30-9 in preseason opener
articles.description: — Jarrett Stidham threw two TD passes following a lackluster performance from Bo Nix and Denver's starters, and the Broncos beat the San Francisco 49ers 30-9 in the preseason opener Saturday night.

images.name: Jarrett Stidham goes deep to Trent Sherfield Sr. for a TD
images.caption: Jarrett Stidham throws a 36-yard touchdown pass to Trent Sherfield Sr. to extend the Broncos' lead.

articles.headline: One pass, one TD: Mahomes, Chiefs get off to good start in 20-17 preseason loss to Cardinals
articles.description: — Quarterback Patrick Mahomes spent some time before Saturday's preseason game running up and down the Kansas City Chiefs sideline, yelling, jumping and psyching himself up for his first game action since last season's Super Bowl.

images.name: Mahomes throws a TD but Chiefs fall to Cardinals
images.caption: Patrick Mahomes' lone pass is a touchdown, but the Cardinals come back to beat the Chiefs.
